divs: sighting detailsi was in my back garden having a cigarette and i looked at one star and imediately noticed a very bright white orb\sphere coming directly over my garden and then slowly go all the way into the distance, it was very low, maximum 1000 feet i would say and was completey silent and very bright and very clear to see, i have a strong set of binoculars and viewed it through them and could only make out a white sphere moving at a steady rate of speed, nothing else, it looked unbelievable, i just dont know what the hell it was, but id love to know, this was one of a few incredible sightings i have had but this was the closest and most clear. i just cant believe what i saw the other night...
